data.oai_dc:dc: Trap-entry times for Peromyscus leucopus collected over one 4-night trapping session during spring 2017, and two 4-night trapping sessions during fall 2017. Mice were trapped in plots invaded by buckthorn (Rhamnus cathartica) and plots with buckthorn removed.
